  "instructions": [
    "Preheat your oven to 200°C (392°F).",
    "In a small bowl, mix together the unsalted pistachio, all-purpose flour, oregano, salt, paprika, and pepper.",
    "Transfer the mixture onto a parchment-lined baking sheet. Press it down evenly with your hand so that it becomes slightly flattened.",
    "Bake in the preheated oven for 15-20 minutes or until golden brown and crispy on top.",
    "Remove from oven and let it cool completely before serving."
